Product description

100% WATERPROOF AND DUSTPROOF

Meets IP67 international standards, no worries with rain, dirt or snow; Drop it in your pool, lake or ocean - no worries, it floats; Audio sources include Bluetooth, AM, FM or wired AUX-IN

120 WATTS PEAK OUTPUT

Amplifier powers an 8-inch full range main driver speaker, a 3-inch tweeter and an oval passive subwoofer for a balanced sound with crisp highs, clear vocals, warm midrange, and deep bass; ECOCAST compatible - pair up to 50 units together within 30-feet of each other for TruWireless Stereo Sound (TWS) and the ultimate party

DRY STORAGE

A large, spacious, watertight dry storage for your phone, keys, and more; External music and phone buttons enable full control while your devices are safely stored inside; A Qi Wireless charging pad for convenient smartphone charging and fast 5V, 2.1A USB output port to charge all your USB compatible devices

BATTERY LASTS FOR DAYS

Play continuously on standard AC plug-in power, or built-in battery for 10+ hours at full volume and up to 50+ hours at average listening levels; Battery fully re-charges in 7-8 hours

DUAL CUP HOLDERS & BOTTLE OPENER

Holds up to two large mugs and there's even a bottle opener. Perfect for outdoor parties!

From the brand

Original waterproof audio co.

ECOXGEAR is with you on all of lifes adventures. To the beach, hunting, tubing, and hanging in your backyard with family and friends

  2. Built for lifes adventures

  3. Proud American Company

    ECOXGEAR has offices in California, Texas and Florida housing our engineering, marketing, warehousing, and tech teams

  4. Hanging out on the San Diego beaches and hiking the hills, Jim and Greg wanted to listen to their music in outdoor environments. This was the birth of ECOXGEAR, The Original Waterproof Audio company.

    We launched our first IP67 waterproof and rugged speaker in 2007. Since then, the ECOXGEAR team has launched dozens of speakers with cutting edge features for all of lifes adventures.

  5. What problem are we solving?

    We added ruggedness and waterproofing to incredibly loud quality portable speakers for the great outdoors.

    How did we get our start?

    Jim and Greg were friends working in a tech start up and were tired of the corporate grind. When Apple and Samsung launched smartphones, how audio is listened to would forever change, and they wanted to lead the movement.

    What makes our products unique?

    Founded in 2007 ECOXGEAR is the original waterproof speaker company. We have been awarded over a dozen US patents solidifying ECOXGEAR as the inventors of this category.
